DEPENDENCIES (Mac):
    xcode
    xcode dev tools (gcc, etc...)
    macports
    macports install avr-gcc
    /Applications/Arduino.app   (get this from http://arduino.cc/en/Main/Software)

NEW ARDUINO PROJECT:
    touch ./<newprojectname>/<newprojectname.ino
    cp Makefile ./<newprojectname>/

VIM C SYNTAX HIGHLIGHTING (.vimrc):
    au BufReadPost *.ino set syntax=c

DEBUGGING:
    Use arduino "Serial Monitor" program for debugging output...easier than setting up /dev/tty.usbmodemXXXXX to read serial in
